ReferencesAndLinks: Gabitov, E., Manor D., and Karni, A. (2015). Patterns of modulation in the activity and connectivity of motor cortex during the repeated generation of movement sequences. Journal of Cognitive Neuroscience, 27(4), 736 – 751.

task-TrainedHandTrainedSequence_bold.jso.TaskDescription: Finger-to-thumb opposition sequence performed with the trained hand using the pre-trained sequence.

task-TrainedHandUntrainedSequence_bold.j.TaskDescription: Finger-to-thumb opposition sequence performed with the trained hand using the novel, untrained sequence.

task-UntrainedHandTrainedSequence_bold.j.TaskDescription: Finger-to-thumb opposition sequence performed with the untrained hand using the pre-trained sequence.

task-UntrainedHandUntrainedSequence_bold.TaskDescription: Finger-to-thumb opposition sequence performed with the untrained hand using the novel, untrained sequence.
